#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This is the musicset that will be used.  Changing this is the same as using "
"the -m command-line parameter."
msgstr ""
"Seo seata nam fuaimean a thèid a chleachdadh. Bidh an dearbh bhuaidh ann ma "
