#: client/options.cpp:1490
msgid "Draw shield graphics for units"
msgstr "Tarraing grafaigean nan sgiathan airson aonadan"

#: client/options.cpp:1491
msgid ""
"Setting this option will draw a shield icon as the flags on units.  If "
"unset, the full flag will be drawn."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, thèid ìomhaigheag sgèith a shealltainn "
"an àite nam brataichean air an h-aonadan. Ma chuireas tu dheth seo, chì thu "
"a' bhratach iomlan."

#: client/options.cpp:1496
msgid "Draw the units in focus"
msgstr "Tarraing na h-aonadan a tha san fhòcas"

#: client/options.cpp:1497
msgid ""
"Setting this option will cause the currently focused unit(s) to always be "
"drawn, even if units are not otherwise being drawn (for instance if 'Draw "
"the units' is unset)."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, thèid na h-aonadan a tharraing a tha san "
"fhòcas, fiù mura dèid aonadan eile a tharraing (mar eisimpleir ma chuir thu "
"dheth 'Tarraing na h-aonadan'). "

#: client/options.cpp:1502
msgid "Draw the fog of war"
msgstr "Tarraing ceò a' chogaidh"

#: client/options.cpp:1503
msgid "Setting this option will draw the fog of war."
msgstr "Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, chithear ceò a' chogaidh."

#: client/options.cpp:1506
msgid "Draw the borders"
msgstr "Tarraing na crìochan"

#: client/options.cpp:1507
msgid "Setting this option will draw the national borders."
msgstr "Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, chithear na crìochan nàiseanta."

#: client/options.cpp:1511
msgid "Draw whether tiles are native to selected unit"
msgstr "Tarraing an e leacagan tùsail a tha annta gus nach eil"

#: client/options.cpp:1513
msgid ""
"Setting this option will highlight tiles that the currently selected unit "
"cannot enter unaided due to non-native terrain. (If multiple units are "
"selected, only tiles that all of them can enter are indicated.)"
msgstr ""
"Ma thaghas tu an roghainn seo, thèid na leacagan a shoilleireachadh nach "
"urrainn dhan aonad a thagh thu a dhol a-steach orra gun taic air sgàth "
"talamh non-native. (Ma thagh thu iomadh aonad, cha dèid ach leacagan a "
"chomharrachadh as urrainn dhaibh uile a dhol a-steach orra.)"

#: client/options.cpp:1519
msgid "Show dead players in Nations report"
msgstr "Seall cluicheadairean marbha ann an aithisg nan nàiseanan"

#: client/options.cpp:1520
msgid ""
"This option controls whether defeated nations are shown on the Nations "
"report page."
msgstr ""
"'S urrainn dhut suidheachadh an-seo an dèid nàisean a chaill a shealltainn "
"air duilleag aithisg nan nàiseanan."

#: client/options.cpp:1523
msgid "Scale fonts when zooming"
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1524
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When this option is set, the fonts and city descriptions will be scaled when "
"the map is zoomed."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an roghainn seo an comas, nithear fòcas air a' mhapa nuair a "
"ghluaiseas a' chuileag os a chionn."

#: client/options.cpp:1529
msgid "Sound bell at new turn"
msgstr "Seirm clag nuair a thòisicheas cuairt ùr"

#: client/options.cpp:1530
msgid ""
"Set this option to have a \"bell\" event be generated at the start of a new "
"turn.  You can control the behavior of the \"bell\" event by editing the "
"message options."
msgstr ""
"Tagh an roghainn seo ma tha thu airson clag a sheirm gach turas a "
"thòisicheas cuairt ùr. Tha smachd agad air na nì a' chlag 's tu a' "
"deasachadh roghainnean teachdaireachd a' chluig."

#: client/options.cpp:1537
msgid "Unit movement animation time (milliseconds)"
msgstr "Àm beothachadh gluasad nan aonad (mili-dhiogan)"

#: client/options.cpp:1538
msgid ""
"This option controls how long unit \"animation\" takes when a unit moves on "
"the map view.  Set it to 0 to disable animation entirely."
msgstr ""
"Tha an roghainn seo a' cumail smachd air an àm a bheir beothachadh de "
"dh'aonad nuair a ghluaiseas e air a' mhapa. Cuir seo gu 0 gus casg a chur "
"air a' bheothachadh gu tur."

#: client/options.cpp:1544
msgid "Mapview recentering time (milliseconds)"
msgstr "Àm ath mheadhanachadh sealladh a' mhapa (milli-dhiogan)"

#: client/options.cpp:1545
msgid ""
"When the map view is recentered, it will slide smoothly over the map to its "
"new position.  This option controls how long this slide lasts.  Set it to 0 "
"to disable mapview sliding entirely."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a thèid sealladh a' mhapa ath mheadhanachadh, slaodaidh e thairis air "
"a' mhapa gu rèidh gun ionad ùr. Tha an roghainn seo a' cumail smachd air dè "
"cho fada 's bheir an gluasad seo. Cuir seo gu 0 gus slaodadh an t-seallaidh "
"a chur à comas gu tur. "

#: client/options.cpp:1552
msgid "Combat animation step time (milliseconds)"
msgstr "Àm beothachadh gluasad na sabaide (mili-dhiogan)"

#: client/options.cpp:1553
msgid ""
"This option controls the speed of combat animation between units on the "
"mapview.  Set it to 0 to disable animation entirely."
msgstr ""
"Tha an roghainn seo a' cumail smachd air astar a' bheothachaidh sabaid eadar "
"aonadan. Cuir seo gu 0 gus casg a chur air a' bheothachadh gu tur."

#: client/options.cpp:1558
msgid "Show icons in the technology tree"
msgstr "Seall na h-ìomhaigheagan air craobh an teicneolais"

#: client/options.cpp:1559
msgid ""
"Setting this option will display icons on the technology tree diagram. "
"Turning this option off makes the technology tree more compact."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, chì thu ìomhaigheagan air craobh an "
"teicneolais. Bidh craobh an teicneolais nas dùmhaile ma chuireas tu dheth an "
"roghainn seo."

#: client/options.cpp:1565
msgid "Use curved lines in the technology tree"
msgstr "Cleachd loidhnichean lùbte air craobh an teicneolais"

#: client/options.cpp:1566
msgid ""
"Setting this option make the technology tree diagram use curved lines to "
"show technology relations. Turning this option off causes the lines to be "
"drawn straight."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, chì thu loidhnichean lùbte air craobh an "
"teicneolais a sheallas dhut na dàimhean eatarra. Ma chuireas tu dheth an "
"roghainn seo, thèid loidhnichean dìreach a chleachdadh 'nan àite."

#: client/options.cpp:1573
msgid "Color to highlight your player/user name"
msgstr ""
"Cleachd dath gus ainm do chluicheadair/do chleachdaiche a shoillseachadh"

#: client/options.cpp:1574
msgid ""
"If set, your player and user name in the new chat messages will be "
"highlighted using this color as background.  If not set, it will just not "
"highlight anything."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu seo, nochdaidh an dath seo air cùlaibh d' ainm "
"cluicheadair is cleachdaiche ann an teachdaireachdan cabadaich ùra. Mura "
"suidhich thu seo, cha dèid càil a shoillseachadh. "

#: client/options.cpp:1579
msgid "Manual Turn Done in AI mode"
msgstr "Deireadh cuairte de làimh ann am modh na h-IF"

#: client/options.cpp:1580
msgid ""
"Disable this option if you do not want to press the Turn Done button "
"manually when watching an AI player."
msgstr ""
"Cuir an roghainn seo à comas mur eil thu ag iarraidh am putan \"Cuairt "
"deiseil\" a bhriogadh a làimh nuair a bhios tu a' coimhead air cluicheadair "
"na h-Inntinne Fhuadain."

#: client/options.cpp:1584
msgid "Auto center on units"
msgstr "Fèin-mheadhanaich air aonadan"

#: client/options.cpp:1585
msgid ""
"Set this option to have the active unit centered automatically when the unit "
"focus changes."
msgstr ""
"Suidhich an roghainn seo ma tha thu ag iarraidh gun dèid an t-aonad "
"gnìomhach a chur sa mheadhan gu fèin-obrachail nuair a ghluaisear gu aonad "
"eile."

#: client/options.cpp:1588
#, fuzzy
msgid "Show automated units"
msgstr "Aonadan ris a bheil taic"

#: client/options.cpp:1589
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Disable this option if you do not want to see automated units autocentered "
"and animated."
msgstr ""
"Cuir an roghainn seo à comas mur eil thu ag iarraidh am putan \"Cuairt "
"deiseil\" a bhriogadh a làimh nuair a bhios tu a' coimhead air cluicheadair "
"na h-Inntinne Fhuadain."

#: client/options.cpp:1593
msgid "Auto center on combat"
msgstr "Fèin-mheadhanaich air sabaid"

#: client/options.cpp:1594
msgid ""
"Set this option to have any combat be centered automatically.  Disabling "
"this will speed up the time between turns but may cause you to miss combat "
"entirely."
msgstr ""
"Suidhich an roghainn seo ma tha thu ag iarraidh gun dèid sabaid sam bith a "
"chur sa mheadhan gu fèin-obrachail. Bidh an t-àm eadar cuairtean nas giorra "
"ach faodaidh gun seachain thu sabaidean ma chuireas tu seo à comas."

#: client/options.cpp:1599
msgid "Auto center on new turn"
msgstr "Fèin-mheadhanaich gach cuairt ùr"

#: client/options.cpp:1600
msgid ""
"Set this option to have the client automatically recenter the map on a "
"suitable location at the start of each turn."
msgstr ""
"Suidhich an roghainn seo ma tha thu ag iarraidh gun gluais an cliant gu àite "
"freagarrach e fhèin aig toiseach gach cuairt."

#: client/options.cpp:1604
msgid "Focus on awakened units"
msgstr "Dèan fòcas air aonadan air an dùsgadh"

#: client/options.cpp:1605
msgid "Set this option to have newly awoken units be focused automatically."
msgstr ""
"Suidhich an roghainn seo ma tha thu ag iarraidh gun dèanar fòcas air aonadan "
"a tha dìreach air dùsgadh gu fèin-obrachail."

#: client/options.cpp:1609
msgid "Keyboardless goto"
msgstr "RachGu as aonais meur-chlàir"

#: client/options.cpp:1610
msgid ""
"If this option is set then a goto may be initiated by left-clicking and then "
"holding down the mouse button while dragging the mouse onto a different tile."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhich thu an roghainn seo, 's urrainn dhut òrdugh RachGu a thoirt le "
"briogadh clì 's tu a' cumail sìos putan na luchaige fhad 's a shlaodas tu a' "
"chuileag do leacag eadar-dhealaichte."

#: client/options.cpp:1616
msgid "Allow goto into the unknown"
msgstr "Ceadaich goto a dh'àitichean fo dhubhar"

#: client/options.cpp:1617
msgid ""
"Setting this option will make the game consider moving into unknown tiles.  "
"If not, then goto routes will detour around or be blocked by unknown tiles."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, beachdaichidh an geama air gluasad a-"
"steach do dh'àitichean fo dhubhar. Mura suidhich thu seo, gluaisidh aonadan "
"air slighe goto mun cuairt air leacagan fo dhubhar no thèid an dùnadh a-"
"steach leotha."

#: client/options.cpp:1622
msgid "Center map when popup city"
msgstr "Fèin-mheadhanaich am mapa air priob-uinneagan baile"

#: client/options.cpp:1623
msgid ""
"Setting this option makes the mapview center on a city when its city dialog "
"is popped up."
msgstr ""
"Ma thaghas tu an roghainn seo, gluaisidh am mapa còmhradh a' bhaile gu "
"meadhan an t-seallaidh nuair a dh'fhosglas an uinneag."

#: client/options.cpp:1628
msgid "Show messages from previous turn"
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1629
msgid ""
"Message Window shows messages also from previous turn. This makes sure you "
"don't miss messages received in the end of the turn, just before the window "
"gets cleared."
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1635
msgid "Concise city production"
msgstr "Gearr-chunntas cinneasachadh a' bhaile"

#: client/options.cpp:1636
msgid ""
"Set this option to make the city production (as shown in the city dialog) to "
"be more compact."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, bidh an cunntas air cinneasachadh a' "
"bhaile nas dùmhaile (mar a chithear e ann an còmhradh a' bhaile)."

#: client/options.cpp:1640
msgid "End turn when done moving"
msgstr "Cuir crìoch air a' chuairt as dèidh a' ghluasaid mu dheireadh"

#: client/options.cpp:1641
msgid ""
"Setting this option makes your turn end automatically when all your units "
"are done moving."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, thig do chuairt gu crìoch leis fhèin "
"nuair a bhios gach aonad agad air gluasad."

#: client/options.cpp:1645
msgid "Prompt for city names"
msgstr "Faighnich dè an t-ainm a chuirear air baile"

#: client/options.cpp:1646
msgid ""
"Disabling this option will make the names of newly founded cities be chosen "
"automatically by the server."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an roghainn seo à comas, thèid ainmean nam bailtean ùra a "
"stèidhicheas tu a thaghadh leis an fhrithealaiche."

#: client/options.cpp:1650
msgid "Pop up city dialog for new cities"
msgstr "Fosgail còmhradh a' bhaile nuair a stèidhear baile ùr"

#: client/options.cpp:1651
msgid ""
"Setting this option will pop up a newly-founded city's city dialog "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, thèid uinneag fhosgladh gu fèin-"
"obrachail a sheallas còmhradh a' bhaile ùir."

#: client/options.cpp:1655
#, fuzzy
msgid "Pop up caravan and spy actions"
msgstr "Fosgail gnìomhan nan carabhanaichean"

#: client/options.cpp:1656
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, when a unit arrives at a city where it can "
"perform an action like establishing a trade route, helping build a wonder, "
"or establishing an embassy, a window will pop up asking which action should "
"be performed. Disabling this option means you will have to do the action "
"manually by pressing either 'r' (for a trade route), 'b' (for building a "
"wonder) or 'd' (for a spy action) when the unit is in the city."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an gnìomh an roghainn seo, chì thu priob-uinneag a "
"dh'fhaighnicheas dhìot dè bu mhath leat dèanamh nuair a ruigeas carabhan no "
"aonad d' a leithid baile far an urrainn dhaibh slighe malairt a "
"stèidheachadh no taic a chur ri mìorbhail. Ma chuireas tu an roghainn seo à "
"comas, feumaidh tu seo a dhèanamh de làimh ('s tu a' briogadh \"r\" airson "
"slighe malairt no \"b\" gus mìorbhail a thogail) nuair a ruigeas an t-aonad "
"am baile."

#: client/options.cpp:1667
#, fuzzy
msgid "Pop up attack questions"
msgstr "Iarrtas priob-uinneige"

#: client/options.cpp:1668
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, when a unit arrives at a target it can attack, a "
"window will pop up asking which action should be performed even if an attack "
"action is legal and no other interesting action are. This allows you to "
"change your mind or to select an uninteresting action."
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1677
msgid "Pop up actions last move to allied"
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1678
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled the final move in a unit's orders to a tile with "
"allied units or cities it can perform an action to is interpreted as an "
"attempted action. This makes the action selection dialog pop up while the "
"unit is at the adjacent tile. This can, in cases where the action requires "
"that the actor unit has moves left, save a turn. The down side is that the "
"unit remains adjacent to rather than inside the protection of an allied city "
"or unit stack."
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1689
msgid "Enable cursor changing"
msgstr "Cuir an comas caochladh na cuileige"

#: client/options.cpp:1690
msgid ""
"This option controls whether the client should try to change the mouse "
"cursor depending on what is being pointed at, as well as to indicate changes "
"in the client or server state."
msgstr ""
"Tha an roghainn seo a' suidheachadh am feuch an cliant cuileag na luchaige a "
"chaochladh a-rèir na tha thu a' tomhadh air agus a-rèir nan diofar rudan a "
"nì an cliant no staid an fhrithealaiche."

#: client/options.cpp:1696
msgid "Select cities before units"
msgstr "Tagh bailtean ro na h-aonadan"

#: client/options.cpp:1697
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, when both cities and units are present in the "
"selection rectangle, only cities will be selected. See the help on Controls."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an comas an roghainn seo, cha dèid a thaghadh ach bailtean "
"nuair a bhios an dà chuid bailtean is aonadan ann an ceàrnag an taghaidh. "
"Faic cobhair leis na h-uidheaman-smachd."

#: client/options.cpp:1702
msgid "Clear unit orders on selection"
msgstr "Falamhaich òrduighean nan aonadan nuair a thèid an taghadh"

#: client/options.cpp:1703
msgid ""
"Enabling this option will cause unit orders to be cleared as soon as one or "
"more units are selected. If this option is disabled, busy units will not "
"stop their current activity when selected. Giving them new orders will clear "
"their current ones; pressing <space> once will clear their orders and leave "
"them selected, and pressing <space> a second time will dismiss them."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an comas an roghainn seo, thèid òrduighean nan aonadan "
"fhalamhadh nuair a thaghas tu aonan no barrachd dhiubh. Ma chuireas tu à "
"comas an roghainn seo, cha sguir aonadan dhe na bhios iad ris nuair a "
"thaghas tu iad. Ma bheir thu òrdugh ùr dhaibh, thèid iad an àite na "
"feadhainn làithreach; ma phutas tu <space> aon turas, thèid an cuid "
"òrduighean fhalamhadh agus bidh iad air an taghadh fhathast agus ma phutas "
"tu air <space> turas eile, gluaisidh tu air adhart."

#: client/options.cpp:1712
msgid "Enable vote bar"
msgstr "Cuir an comas bàr nam bhòtaichean"

#: client/options.cpp:1713
msgid ""
"If this option is turned on, the vote bar will be displayed to show vote "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu air an roghainn seo, chithear bàr nam bhòtaichean air am "
"faicear fiosrachadh bhòtaidh."

#: client/options.cpp:1717
msgid "Always display the vote bar"
msgstr "Seall bàr nam bhòtaichean an-còmhnaidh"

#: client/options.cpp:1718
msgid ""
"If this option is turned on, the vote bar will never be hidden, even if "
"there is no running vote."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu air an roghainn seo, chithear bàr nam bhòtaichean an-"
"còmhnaidh fiù mur eil bhòt a' dol."

#: client/options.cpp:1723
msgid "Do not show vote bar if not a player"
msgstr "Na seall bàr nam bhòtaichean mur eil thu 'nad chluicheadair"

#: client/options.cpp:1724
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, the client won't show the vote bar if you are not "
"a player."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an roghainn seo an comas, cha nochd an cliant bàr nam "
"bhòtaichean mur eil thu 'nad chluicheadair."

#: client/options.cpp:1728
msgid "Set new votes at front"
msgstr "Cuir na bhòtaichean ùra gun toiseach"

#: client/options.cpp:1729
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, then new votes will go to the front of the vote "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an roghainn seo an comas, nochdaidh na bhòtaichean ùra aig "
"toiseach liosta nam bhòtaichean."

#: client/options.cpp:1734
msgid "Autoaccept tileset suggestions"
msgstr "Gabh ri molaidhean a thaobh sheataichean leacagan gu fèin-obrachail"

#: client/options.cpp:1735
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, any tileset suggested by the ruleset is "
"automatically used; otherwise you are prompted to change tileset."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an comas an roghainn seo, gabhar ri seata leacagan sam bith "
"gu fèin-obrachail a mholas seata nan riaghailtean; mur an cuir, thèid "
"iarraidh ort seata nan leacagan atharrachadh."

#: client/options.cpp:1740
msgid "Enable sound effects"
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1741
msgid ""
"Play sound effects, assuming there's suitable sound plugin and soundset with "
"the sounds."
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1745
msgid "Enable in-game music"
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1746
msgid ""
"Play music during the game, assuming there's suitable sound plugin and "
"musicset with in-game tracks."
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1750
msgid "Enable menu music"
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1751
msgid ""
"Play music while not in actual game, assuming there's suitable sound plugin "
"and musicset with menu music tracks."
msgstr ""

