msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an comas an roghainn seo, gabhar ri seata leacagan sam bith "
"gu fèin-obrachail a mholas seata nan riaghailtean; mur an cuir, thèid "
"iarraidh ort seata nan leacagan atharrachadh."

#: client/options.cpp:1767
#, fuzzy
msgid "Autoaccept musicset suggestions"
msgstr "Gabh ri molaidhean a thaobh sheataichean leacagan gu fèin-obrachail"

#: client/options.cpp:1768
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, any musicset suggested by the ruleset is "
