msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu an comas an roghainn seo, gabhar ri seata leacagan sam bith "
"gu fèin-obrachail a mholas seata nan riaghailtean; mur an cuir, thèid "
"iarraidh ort seata nan leacagan atharrachadh."

#: client/options.cpp:1773
msgid "Background layer"
msgstr "Breath a' chùlaibh"

#: client/options.cpp:1774
msgid "The background layer of the overview shows just ocean and land."
msgstr ""
"Cha seall breath a' chùlaibh ach cuantan is talamh san fhoir-shealladh."

#: client/options.cpp:1778
msgid "Terrain relief map layer"
msgstr "Mapa breath rilif na talamhainn"

#: client/options.cpp:1779
msgid "The relief layer shows all terrains on the map."
msgstr ""
"Tha breath na rilife a' sealltainn gach seòrsa talamhainn air a' mhapa."

#: client/options.cpp:1782
msgid "Borders layer"
msgstr "Breath nan crìochan"

#: client/options.cpp:1783
msgid ""
"The borders layer of the overview shows which tiles are owned by each player."
msgstr ""
"Tha breath nan crìochan a' sealltainn dè na leacagan a tha aig gach "
"cluicheadair san fhoir-shealladh."

#: client/options.cpp:1787
msgid "Borders layer on ocean tiles"
msgstr "Breath nan crìochan air leacagan na mara"

#: client/options.cpp:1788
msgid ""
"The borders layer of the overview are drawn on ocean tiles as well (this may "
"look ugly with many islands). This option is only of interest if you have "
"set the option \"Borders layer\" already."
msgstr ""
"Thèid breath nan crìochan a tharraing air leacagan a' chuain cuideachd san "
"fhoir-shealladh ach faodaidh nach bi coltas tarraingeach air ma tha pailteas "
"eileanan agad. Cha bhi an roghainn seo gu feum dhut ach ma shuidhich thu an "
"roghainn \"Breath nan crìochaǹ\" mu thràth."

#: client/options.cpp:1793
msgid "Units layer"
msgstr "Breath nan aonadan"

#: client/options.cpp:1794
msgid "Enabling this will draw units on the overview."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu seo an comas, thèid na h-aonadan a tharraing san fhoir-"
"shealladh."

#: client/options.cpp:1796
msgid "Cities layer"
msgstr "Breath nam bailtean"

#: client/options.cpp:1797
msgid "Enabling this will draw cities on the overview."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu seo an comas, thèid na bailtean a tharraing san fhoir-"
"shealladh."

#: client/options.cpp:1799
msgid "Overview fog of war"
msgstr "Ceò a' chogaidh san fhoir-shealladh"

#: client/options.cpp:1800
msgid "Enabling this will show fog of war on the overview."
msgstr ""
"Ma chuireas tu seo an comas, thèid ceò a' chogaidh a shealltainn san fhoir-"
"shealladh."

#: client/options.cpp:1849
msgid ""
"If this option is set the client will use the whole screen area for drawing."
msgstr ""
"Ma shuidhicheas tu an roghainn seo, cleachdaidh an cliant an sgrìn gu lèir."

#: client/options.cpp:1853
#, fuzzy
msgid "Show titlebar"
msgstr "Seall na bailtean"

#: client/options.cpp:1854
msgid ""
"If this option is set the client will show a titlebar. If disabled, then no "
"titlebar will be shown, and minimize/maximize/etc buttons will be placed on "
"the menu bar."
msgstr ""

#: client/options.cpp:1859
