"cities (including the capital) have a modest amount of corruption."
msgstr ""
"Chan atharraich coirbteachd a-rèir an astair on phrìomh bhaile ann an co-"
"mhaoineas; chan eil ach ìre mheadhanach de choirbteachd anns gach baile (a' "
"gabhail a-steach a' phìomh bhaile."

