msgid ""
"Egypt was the second-oldest of the world's civilizations.  Since ancient "
"times it has been unusually urbanized, supporting a large population on silt "
"deposited by the annual floodings of the Nile."
msgstr ""
"'S e an dàrna sìobhaltas as sine air uachdar an t-saoghail a tha san Èiphit. "
"Bha àireamh neo-àbhaisteach dhe na h-Èiphitich a' fuireach ann am bailtean o "
"chionn fhada fhada, le sluagh mòr a' faighinn beòshlaint às an eabar a "
"dh'fhàgas tuiltean na Nìle gach bliadhna."

