#: data/civ1/nations.ruleset:1339 data/civ2/nations.ruleset:1677
msgid ""
"Rome was, in legend, founded by Romulus in 753 BC. At its height, Rome "
"controlled nearly all of Europe, northern Africa and Mesopotamia."
msgstr ""
"Chaidh an Ròimh a chur air bhonn le Romulus ann an 753 RC a-rèir nam fionn-"
"sgeulan. Bha smachd aig an Ròimh air cha mhòr an Roinn-Eòrpa, Afraga a Tuath "
"agus Mesopotamia air fad nuair a bha i ag àirde a neirt."

