"Since the dawn of civilization, barbarians have been a threat to cultured "
"peoples everywhere."
msgstr ""
"Bha borbaich 'na chunnart do chultaran àite sam bith o thoiseach an t-"
"sìobhaltais."

#: data/civ1/nations.ruleset:1601 data/civ2/nations.ruleset:2196
