#: data/civ2/governments.ruleset:77
msgid ""
"Anarchy offers slightly less corruption and waste than Despotism, but "
"slightly more unhappiness."
msgstr ""
"Tha beagan nas lugha de choirbteachd is ana-caitheamh ann fo ain-riaghailt "
"ach beagan a bharrachd mì-thoileachais an coimeas ri ain-tighearnas."

#: data/civ2/governments.ruleset:97
msgid ""
"Despotism suffers the highest level of corruption and waste of all forms of "
"government."
msgstr ""
"Tha an ìre as àirde de choirbteachd is ana-caitheamh ann fo ain-tighearnas "
"am measg nan riaghaltasan uile."

#: data/civ2/governments.ruleset:119
msgid ""
"Monarchy suffers the same small amount of corruption and waste that the "
"Republic does."
msgstr ""
"Tha an dearbh ìre bheag de choirbteachd is ana-caitheamh ann am monarcachd "
"'s tha ann am poblachd."

#: data/civ2/governments.ruleset:142
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Under Communism, corruption and waste does not vary by distance from the "
"capital. All cities, including the capital, have a modest amount of "
"corruption."
msgstr ""
"Chan atharraich coirbteachd is ana-caitheamh a-rèir an astair on phrìomh "
"bhaile ann an co-mhaoineas; chan eil ach ìre mheadhanach de choirbteachd "
"anns gach baile (a' gabhail a-steach a' phìomh bhaile."

#: data/civ2/governments.ruleset:151 data/civ2/techs.ruleset:362
