#: data/civ2/nations.ruleset:1831 data/nation/sioux.ruleset:8
msgid ""
"The Sioux was a North American nation that fought several decisive battles "
"against the United States. It consisted of three distinct groups of tribes: "
"the Lakota, the Dakota and the Nakota."
msgstr ""
"'S e nàisean de thùsanaich ann an Aimeireaga a Tuath a bha sna Seachd "
"Teintean Comhairle (Sioux na Beurla) agus thug iad buaidh air na Stàitean "
