#: data/civ2/nations.ruleset:1925 data/nation/spanish.ruleset:8
msgid ""
"The modern Spanish nation was formed when the rulers of the kingdoms of "
"Castile and Aragon led the recapture of the Iberian peninsula from the "
"Moslems. The Reconquista was completed in 1492, the same year Columbus "
"sailed. Spain then went on to create an empire on which the sun never set."
msgstr ""
"Chaidh an nàisean Spàinnteach mar a tha sinne eòlach air a chruthachadh "
"nuair a thug rìoghachdan Castilla is León buaidh air na Muslamaich 's iad "
"airson ceann-tìre na h-Ìbeire ath ghlacadh uapa. Thàinig an Reconquista gu "
"crìoch ann an 1492, an dearbh bhliadhna a sheòl Colombo air tòir an t-"
"saoghail ùir. Thog an Spàinnt impire an uairsin a bha cho mòr 's nach do "
"laigh a' ghrian ann a-riamh."

