#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2358
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A Spy can also be used to:\n"
"\n"
" - sabotage an enemy unit reducing its hitpoints to half, if it is alone on "
"a tile and the players are at war;\n"
" - poison the water supply of an enemy city (reducing the population by "
"one);\n"
" - steal specific technology, with a reduced chance of success;\n"
" - steal further technologies from a city which has already been stolen "
"from. Cities become more resistant each time they are stolen from;\n"
" - sabotage predetermined city targets (with a reduced chance of success)."
msgstr ""
"Nì thu na leanas le brathadair cuideachd:\n"
" - sabotais air aonad nàimhdeil (a' sgriosadh an dàrna leth dhe phuingean "
"beatha), ma tha e air leacag leis fhèin agus ma tha an dà chluicheadair a' "
"cogadh ri chèile;\n"
" - puinnsean a chur ann an uisge de bhaile (a' lùghdachadh sluagh a' bhaile "
"le aonan agus a' falamhadh na sìol-lainn);\n"
" - teicneolas àraidh a ghoid (le buailteachd soirbheis nas lugha);\n"
" - teicneolas a bharrachd a ghoird air baile a ghoid thu teicneolas air "
"roimhe (ged a dh'fhàsas bailtean nas fhearr air dìon o ghoid mar sin gach "
"turas a ghoideas tu rud);\n"
" - sabotais air targaid àraidh sa bhaile (le buailteachd soirbheis nas "
"lugha)."

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2374 data/royale/units.ruleset:2897
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2449
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Spies built under Communist or Federation governments will start at the "
"first veteran level (handler)."
msgstr ""
"Tòisichidh gach brathadair air a' chiad leibheil de sheann ghaisgeachd ma "
"thèid a thogail fo riaghaltas Comannach (handler)."

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2406 data/royale/units.ruleset:3127
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2481
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A Caravan carries goods or material for trading with other nations, or to "
"help build wonders in your own cities."
msgstr ""
"Giùlainidh carabhan bathar no stuthan a chum malairt le bailtean is "
"dùthchannan fad air falbh no 's urrainn dha taic a chur ri togail de "
"mhìorbhail 'nad bhailtean."

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2409 data/royale/units.ruleset:3130
msgid ""
"Caravans cannot take advantage of maglevs, but may travel on the railroads "
"that accompany them."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2412 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2488
msgid ""
"A Caravan sent to a foreign city (one not owned by an enemy) can establish a "
"trade route. The route's ongoing revenue is doubled if the two cities "
"involved are on different continents. Each city can support a maximum of two "
"trade routes."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2417 data/royale/units.ruleset:3135
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2493
msgid ""
"A Caravan sent to one of your own cities that is building a wonder can add "
"50 shields towards its production. If your city is not building a wonder, "
"the Caravan can take no special action."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2454 data/royale/units.ruleset:3172
#: data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2530
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Freight unit replaces the Caravan, and moves at twice the speed. It has "
"the same behavior and movement restrictions."
msgstr ""
"Tha an t-aonad frachd a' dol an àite a' charabhain agus tha e dà thuras nas "
"luaithe. Cuiridh gach aonad frachd a chuireas taic ri togail mìorbhail 50 "
"sgiath ris."

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2489 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2565
msgid ""
"Explorers can also perform some actions in another player's city, and like "
"Diplomats and Spies, the unit is not consumed by these harmless actions:"
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2506 data/classic/units.ruleset:2283
#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:2315 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:2370
#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3229 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2582
msgid "?unit:Leader"
msgstr "?unit:Ceannard"

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2540 data/classic/units.ruleset:2317
#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:2349 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:2404
#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3263 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2616
#, fuzzy
msgid "This is you. If you lose this unit, you lose the game. So do not."
msgstr ""
"Seo thusa. Ma chailleas tu an t-aonad seo, caillidh thu an geama. Feuch 's "
"na dèan sin ma-tà!"

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2542 data/classic/units.ruleset:2319
#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:2351 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:2406
#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3265 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2618
#, fuzzy
msgid "Will not unleash barbarians from huts."
msgstr "* Chan fhaod ach borbaich seo a thogail.\n"

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2589 data/classic/units.ruleset:2366
#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:2398 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:2453
#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3312 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2665
msgid "AWACS"
msgstr "AWACS"

#: data/civ2civ3/units.ruleset:2615 data/classic/units.ruleset:2392
#: data/experimental/units.ruleset:2424 data/multiplayer/units.ruleset:2479
#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3338 data/sandbox/units.ruleset:2691
msgid ""
"The AWACS (Airborne Warning and Control System) is an airplane with an "
"advanced radar that can determine the location of enemy units over a wide "
"area."
msgstr ""
"'S e itealan a tha san AWACS (Airborne Warning and Control System) aig a "
"bheil rèidear adhartach a chì aonadan nàimhdeil o fhad air falbh."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:86
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Two cities with Airports can airlift one unit per turn.  Airlifting "
"instantly transports the unit from one city to another and will use all of "
"the unit's movement points. A unit must have some movement points left to be "
"airlifted."
msgstr ""
"'S urrainn do dhà bhaile anns a bheil puirt-adhair togail-adhair a dhèanamh "
"le aon aonad gach cuairt.  Ma nì thu togail-adhair, thèid an t-aonad a "
"ghluasad on dàrna bhaile gun bhaile eile agus cha bhi puingean gluasaid air "
"fhàgail aig an aonad.  Feumaidh puingean gluasaid a bhith aig aonad mus "
"urrainn dhut togail-adhair a dhèanamh leis."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:321
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Entertains the citizens of a city, making 3 unhappy citizens content. (Four "
"after the discovery of Electricity.) However, it does not affect citizens "
"made unhappy by military activity."
msgstr ""
"Bheir seo cuirm dha na saoranaich agus nì e 3 saoranaich mhì-thoilichte "
"riaraichte.  (Ceithir às dèidh dhut dealan a rannsachadh.)  Ge-tà, cha bhi "
"buaidh aig a' choileasam air saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth "
"gnìomhachd an airm."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:347 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reduces the corruption in a city by 50%, and makes the revolt cost of the "
"city 4 times bigger. (These effects are redundant in your capital city.)"
msgstr ""
"Ìslichidh seo coirbteachd ann am baile le 50% agus bidh cosgais aramach a' "
"bhaile 4 tursan nas àirde. (Chan eil a' bhuaidh seo gu feum 'nad phrìomh-"
"bhaile.)"

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:351 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:358
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:352
msgid ""
"Under a Democracy, a Courthouse also makes 1 unhappy citizen content (unless "
"that citizen is unhappy about military activity)."
msgstr ""
"Nì taigh-cùirte 1 saoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte ann an deamocrasaidh "
"(ach saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth gnìomhachd an airm)."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:449 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:478
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:447
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the effect of a Factory and Mfg. Plant on the shield production of "
"a city, and also reduces the amount of pollution generated by that "
"production. A Hydro Plant in combination with either a Factory or Mfg. Plant "
"gives a 75% production bonus over the level without any of these "
"improvements, while giving pollution only 75% of the equivalent combination "
"with a Power Plant. A Hydro Plant, Factory, and Mfg. Plant together give a "
"150% production bonus with pollution only 50% of the equivalent combination "
"with a Power Plant."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud èifeachd an fhactaraidh agus an taighe-saothrachaidh air "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan a' bhaile agus lùghdaichidh seo an truailleadh a "
"dh'èiricheas an cois cinneasachadh a' bhaile.  Cuiridh taigh dealain-uisge "
"am meud cinneasachadh sgiathan le 75% ma bhios factaraidh no taigh-"
"saothrachaidh sa bhaile thar na gheibheadh tu as aonais fhad 's nach fhaigh "
"thu ach 75% dhen truailleadh a gheibheadh tu le taigh-cumhachd ann; "
"gheibhear duais cinneasachaidh 150% an cois taigh dealain-uisge, factaraidh "
"agus taigh-saothrachaidh ann am baile agus duais cinneasachaidh 150% agus "
"chan fhaighear ach 50% de thruailleadh an coimeas ris na bhiodh agad nam "
"biodh taigh-cumhachd ann."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:485 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:540
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increases the science output in a city by 100%."
msgstr "Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh saidheans a' bhaile le 100%."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:507 data/royale/buildings.ruleset:634
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:592
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Increases the luxury good and tax output in a city by 50%."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh sòghalachd is cìsean a' bhaile le 50%."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:581 data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:573
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the effect of a Factory and Mfg. Plant on the shield production of "
"a city, and also reduces the amount of pollution generated by that "
"production. A Nuclear Plant in combination with either a Factory or Mfg. "
"Plant gives a 75% production bonus over the level without any of these "
"improvements, while giving pollution only 75% of the equivalent combination "
"with a Power Plant. A Nuclear Plant, Factory, and Mfg. Plant together give a "
"150% production bonus with pollution only 50% of the equivalent combination "
"with a Power Plant."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud buaidh an fhactaraidh agus an taighe-saothrachaidh air "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan a' bhaile agus lùghdaichidh seo an truailleadh a "
"dh'èiricheas an cois cinneasachadh a' bhaile.  Cuiridh taigh niùclasach am "
"meud cinneasachadh sgiathan le 75% ma bhios factaraidh no taigh-"
"saothrachaidh sa bhaile thar na gheibheadh tu as aonais ach chan fhaigh thu "
"ach 75% dhen truailleadh a gheibheadh tu le taigh-cumhachd ann; gheibhear "
"duais cinneasachaidh 150% an cois taigh niùclasach, factaraidh agus taigh-"
"saothrachaidh ann am baile agus chan fhaighear ach 50% de thruailleadh an "
"coimeas ris na bhiodh agad nam biodh taigh-cumhachd ann."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:651 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:708
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:636 data/royale/buildings.ruleset:785
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:741
msgid ""
"The cost to enemy Diplomats and Spies of inciting a revolt in a city also "
"depends upon the city's distance from the capital (under all forms of "
"government). Your capital city itself cannot be incited to revolt, and "
"enjoys a bonus when enemy agents try to evade your own agents stationed in "
"the city, or sabotage your buildings."
msgstr ""

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:666 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:723
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:651
#, fuzzy, c-format
msgid ""
"Under Despotism the city containing the palace gains a +75% production "
"bonus, and under Monarchy a +50% production bonus."
msgstr ""
"Gheibh am baile far a bheil an lùchairt duais cinneasachaidh de 75% fo ain-"
"tighearnas agus duais cinneasachaidh de 50% fo mhonarcachd."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:741 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:800
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:723
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the effect of a Factory and Mfg. Plant on the shield production of "
"a city. A Power Plant in combination with either a Factory or Mfg. Plant "
"gives a 75% production bonus over the level without any of these "
"improvements. A Power Plant, Factory, and Mfg. Plant together give a 150% "
"production bonus. The extra production may lead to the city generating more "
"pollution."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud buaidh an fhactaraidh agus an taighe-saothrachaidh air "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan a' bhaile. Cuiridh taigh-cumhachd am meud "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan le 75% ma bhios factaraidh no taigh-saothrachaidh sa "
"bhaile thar na gheibheadh tu as aonais; gheibhear duais cinneasachaidh 150% "
"an cois taigh-cumhachd, factaraidh agus taigh-saothrachaidh ann am baile. "
"Faodaidh gun adhbharaich an cinneasachadh a bharrachd seo barrachd "
"truaillidh ann."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:799 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:858
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Together with a Library, a Research Lab increases the science production of "
"a city by 200%. Together with a Library and a University, a Research Lab "
"increases the science production of a city by 450%."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh deuchainn-lann am meud cinneasachadh saidheansail a' bhaile le 200% "
"ma bhios leabhar-lann ann cuideachd. Ma bhios leabhar-lann, oilthigh agus "
"deuchainn-lann ann còmhla, thèid a chur am meud le 450%."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:899 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:958
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:876
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the effect of a Factory and Mfg. Plant on the shield production of "
"a city, and also greatly reduces the amount of pollution generated by that "
"production. A Solar Plant leads to less overall pollution than no plant at "
"all. A Solar Plant in combination with either a Factory or Mfg. Plant gives "
"a 75% production bonus over the level without any of these improvements, "
"while giving pollution only 50% of the equivalent combination with a Power "
"Plant. A Solar Plant, Factory, and Mfg. Plant together give a 150% "
"production bonus, and eliminates all pollution generated by production in "
"that city."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud buaidh an fhactaraidh agus an taighe-saothrachaidh air "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan a' bhaile agus lùghdaichidh seo an truailleadh a "
"dh'èiricheas an cois cinneasachadh a' bhaile gu mòr.  Cuiridh taigh-cumhachd "
"grèine am meud cinneasachadh sgiathan le 75% ma bhios factaraidh no taigh-"
"saothrachaidh sa bhaile thar na gheibheadh tu as an aonais agus chan fhaigh "
"thu ach 50% dhen truailleadh a gheibheadh tu le taigh-cumhachd ann; "
"gheibhear duais cinneasachaidh 150% an cois taigh niùclasach, factaraidh "
"agus taigh-saothrachaidh ann am baile agus cuiridh e às do thruailleadh sam "
"bith a ghineas am baile."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1024
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Together with a Bank, a Stock Exchange boosts tax and luxury good production "
"in a city by 50%. Together with a Marketplace and a Bank, a Stock Exchange "
"boosts tax and luxury good production in a city by 150%."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh margadh-earrannan am meud cinneasachadh chìsean is sòghalachd le 50% "
"sa bhaile ma bhios banca ann cuideachd. Ma bhios banca agus margaid ann "
"cuideachd, cuiridh margadh-earrannan am meud cinneasachadh chìsean is "
"sòghalachd le 150% sa bhaile."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1097 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1159
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1072
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Makes one unhappy citizen content. The Mysticism advance doubles this "
"effect. With both Mysticism and the Oracle, 4 citizens are made content. "
"Does not affect citizens made unhappy by military activity."
msgstr ""
"Nì seo aon saoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte.  Nuair a lorgas tu "
"fàidheantas, thèid a' bhuaidh a dhùblachadh.  Ma bhios fàidheantas agus "
"oracail agad, nì seo riaraichte 4 saoranaich.  Cha bhi buaidh air saoranaich "
"a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth gnìomhachd an airm."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1123 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1187
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Together with a Library, a University increases the science production of a "
"city by 250%."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh saidheans a' bhaile le 250% ma bhios "
"leabhar-lann ann cuideachd."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1145 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1211
#: data/royale/buildings.ruleset:1396 data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1281
msgid ""
"The entire map becomes permanently visible to the player who owns it -- the "
"player always has up-to-date knowledge of all terrain and cities (but not "
"units) despite fog-of-war. It allows all players to start building spaceship "
"parts (assuming they have researched the necessary technologies)."
msgstr ""
"Chì an cluicheadair a thogas seo am mapa air fad -- agus bidh fiosrachadh ùr-"
"nodha aig a' chluicheadair air gach leacag is baile (ach chan ann air "
"aonadan) an dh'aindeoin ceò a' chogaidh. Bheir seo comas dhan a h-uile "
"cluicheadair tòiseachadh air soitheach-fànais a thogail (fhad 's a tha an "
"teicneolas iomchaidh aca)."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1170 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1236
msgid ""
"City improvements which would normally have an upkeep of 1 are free of "
"upkeep, for all your cities."
msgstr ""
"Bidh leasachadh baile sam bith a chosgadh 1 bheòshlaint a ghnàth saor an-"
"sgaidh airson gach baile agad."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1237
msgid ""
"This stunning technological achievement makes one unhappy citizen content in "
"each of your cities (including citizens unhappy about military activity)."
msgstr ""
"Nì an teicneolas iongantach seo aon saoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte anns "
"gach baile agad (a' gabhail a-steach saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air "
"sgàth gnìomhachd an airm)."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1287 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your reputation and goodwill among other nations is recovered twice as fast."
msgstr ""
"Ath chosnaidh tu cliù is deagh ghean nan nàiseanan eile dà thuras nas "
"luaithe leis."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1333
#, fuzzy
msgid "Works as a City Wall in all of your cities."
msgstr "Tha seo mar gum biodh balla baile anns gach baile agad."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1358 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1424
msgid ""
"Makes one content citizen happy in every city. Makes two extra content "
"citizens happy in the city containing the Hanging Gardens (that is, a total "
"of 3). In the unlikely event where there are no content citizens to get the "
"effect of Hanging Gardens, the wonder applies to unhappy citizens (including "
"those unhappy about military activity), making each content then happy."
msgstr ""
"Nì seo aon saoranach riaraichte toilichte anns gach baile. Nì e dà "
"shaoranach riaraichte a bharrachd toilichte sa bhaile far a bheil na Liosan "
"Crochte ('s e sin 3 uile gu lèir). Ged nach tachair seo ro thric, mur eil "
"saoranach riaraichte sam bith ann a sheasas buaidh nan Liosan Crochte, bidh "
"buaidh air saoranaich mhì-thoilichte 'na àite (a' gabhail a-steach an "
"fheadhainn a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth gnìomhachd an airm) agus nì iad "
"riaraichte iad."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1408 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Boosts science production by 100% in every city you control that has a "
"University."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh saidheansail le 100% anns gach baile agad "
"aig a bheil oilthigh."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1430 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1496
msgid ""
"Makes two unhappy citizens content in every city (including citizens unhappy "
"about military activity)."
msgstr ""
"Nì seo dà shaoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte anns gach baile (a' gabhail a-"
"steach saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth gnìomhachd an airm)."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1476 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1542
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1637
#, fuzzy
msgid "Upgrades one obsolete unit per game turn for free."
