#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1522 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1588
msgid "Gives all your sea units 2 additional movement points."
msgstr "Bheir seo 2 phuing gluasaid a bharrachd do gach aonad mara agad."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1613 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1680
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Makes two additional unhappy citizens content in every city with a Temple. "
"Does not affect citizens made unhappy by military activity."
msgstr ""
"Nì seo dà shaoranach mì-thoilichte toilichte anns gach baile sa bheil "
"teampall.  Chan eil buaidh air saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth "
"gnìomhachd an airm."

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:1637 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1704
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The amount of stored food lost when one of your cities grows or shrinks is "
