"Cuiridh banca, còmhla ri margaid, am meud cinneasachadh sòghalachd agus "
"chìsean le 100% ann am baile."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:330
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:542
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:726
msgid "Adds 2 points of culture each turn."
msgstr ""

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:437
msgid "Hospital"
msgstr "Ospadal"

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:453
msgid ""
"A Hospital is used to treat the ill, and sometimes for medical research. A "
"city with a Hospital is less likely to suffer from plagues."
msgstr ""
"Gheibh euslaintich leigheas ann an ospadal agus thèid a chleachdadh airson "
"rannsachadh meadaigeach uaireannan. Tha cunnart plàighe nas lugha ann ma "
"bhios ospadal sa bhaile."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:497
msgid "Genetic Lab"
msgstr "Deuchainn-lann gintinneachd"

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:514
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a Genetic Laboratory medicaments can be researched. The possibility for "
"plagues within the city is reduced."
msgstr ""
"'s urrainn dhut leigheasan a rannsachadh ann an deuchainn-lann gintinneachd. "
"Thèid cunnart phlàighean sa bhaile lùghdachadh.\n"
"Bheir deuchainn-lann gintinneachd comas dhut piseach a thoirt air ginean "
"lusan is bheathaichean. Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh bìdh le 25% ma "
"bhios am baile nas motha na 20."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:517
#, fuzzy, c-format
msgid ""
"A Genetic Laboratory allows the genetic optimization of plants and animals. "
"The food output is increased by 25% if the city size exceeds 20."
msgstr ""
"'s urrainn dhut leigheasan a rannsachadh ann an deuchainn-lann gintinneachd. "
"Thèid cunnart phlàighean sa bhaile lùghdachadh.\n"
"Bheir deuchainn-lann gintinneachd comas dhut piseach a thoirt air ginean "
"lusan is bheathaichean. Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh bìdh le 25% ma "
"bhios am baile nas motha na 20."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:589
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1111
msgid ""
"If a metropolis (city size > 30) has a Mass Transit and a Super Highway the "
"city radius is further increased."
msgstr ""
"Ma tha mòr-chòmhdhail agus sàr-rathaidean aig mòr-bhaile (meud > 30), bidh "
"rèideas nas motha aig a' bhaile."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:641
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the effect of a Factory and Mfg. Plant on the shield production of "
"a city, and also reduces the amount of pollution generated by that "
"production.   Nuclear Plant in combination with either a Factory or Mfg. "
"Plant gives a 75% production bonus over the level without any of these "
"improvements, while giving pollution only 75% of the equivalent combination "
"with a Power Plant. A Nuclear Plant, Factory, and Mfg. Plant together give a "
"150% production bonus with pollution only 50% of the equivalent combination "
"with a Power Plant."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud buaidh an fhactaraidh agus an taighe-saothrachaidh air "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan a' bhaile agus lùghdaichidh seo an truailleadh a "
"dh'èiricheas an cois cinneasachadh a' bhaile.  Cuiridh taigh niùclasach am "
"meud cinneasachadh sgiathan le 75% ma bhios factaraidh no taigh-"
"saothrachaidh sa bhaile thar na gheibheadh tu as aonais ach chan fhaigh thu "
"ach 75% dhen truailleadh a gheibheadh tu le taigh-cumhachd ann; gheibhear "
"duais cinneasachaidh 150% an cois taigh niùclasach, factaraidh agus taigh-"
"saothrachaidh ann am baile agus chan fhaighear ach 50% de thruailleadh an "
"coimeas ris na bhiodh agad nam biodh taigh-cumhachd ann."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:932
msgid ""
"Allows a city to grow larger than size 12. Pre-requirement is an Aqueduct "
"for a city to grow larger than size 8. The Sewer System further reduces the "
"chance of a plague."
msgstr ""
"Bheir seo comas do bhaile fàs nas motha na 12. Feumaidh tu duct-uisge mus "
"fàs baile nas motha na 8. Tha rian shàibhearan a' lùghdachadh cunnart "
"plàighe tuilleadh."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1164
msgid "The work of the priests also reduces the effect of plague in the city."
msgstr ""
"Tha obair nan sagartan a' lùghdachadh buaidh nam plàigh sa bhaile cuideachd."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1190
msgid "Adds 1 point of culture each turn."
msgstr ""

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1303
msgid ""
"This stunning technological achievement makes one unhappy citizen content in "
"each of your cities (including citizens unhappy about military activity). It "
"further reduces the possibility for an illness in the city."
msgstr ""
"Nì an teicneolas iongantach seo aon saoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte anns "
"gach baile agad (a' gabhail a-steach saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air "
"sgàth gnìomhachd an airm). Lùghdaichidh e cunnart tinneis sa bhaile "
"tuilleadh."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1630
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The player who owns it gets an embassy with all players with whom one has "
"ever had contact with."
msgstr ""
"Gheibh an cluicheadair aig a bheil e ambasaid le gach cluicheadair eile."

#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:1796
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All your new military land units start with an additional veteran level. "
"This is cumulative with any Barracks building in a city. With both, units "
"are created as Hardened. The chance of a land unit getting the next veteran "
"level after a battle increases by half."
msgstr ""
"Tòisichidh gach aonad talamhainn ùr an airm air a' chiad leibheil de sheann "
