#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:113 data/royale/buildings.ruleset:435
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:397
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Entertains the citizens of a city, making 3 unhappy citizens content.  (Four "
"after the discovery of Electricity.) However, it does not affect citizens "
"made unhappy by military activity."
msgstr ""
"Bheir seo cuirm dha na saoranaich agus nì e 3 saoranaich mhì-thoilichte "
"riaraichte.  (Ceithir às dèidh dhut dealan a rannsachadh.)  Ge-tà, cha bhi "
"buaidh aig a' choileasam air saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth "
"gnìomhachd an airm."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:299
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"City Walls make it easier to defend a city. They triple the defense strength "
"of units within the city against land and helicopter units.  They are "
"ineffective against airborne and sea units as well as Howitzers. City Walls "
"also prevent the loss of population which occurs when a defending unit is "
"destroyed by a land unit."
msgstr ""
"Bidh e nas fhasa baile a dhìon ma bhios balla baile ann.  Bidh cumhachd dìon "
"de dh'aonadan am broinn baile trì turais nas àirde an aghaidh aonadan "
"talamhainn is heileacoptairean.  Chan eil iad gu feum an aghaidh aonadan "
"adhair is mara agus hòbhaitsearan.  Dìonaidh balla baile ro chall sluaigh "
"cuideachd a thachras nuair a thèid aonad dìon a sgriosadh le aonad "
"talamhainn."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reduces the corruption and waste in a city by 50%, and makes the revolt cost "
"of the city 4 times bigger. (These effects are redundant in your capital "
"city.)"
msgstr ""
"Ìslichidh seo coirbteachd is sgudal ann am baile le 50% agus bidh cosgais "
"reabhlaid a' bhaile 4 tursan nas àirde. (Chan eil a' bhuaidh seo gu feum "
"'nad phrìomh-bhaile.)"

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:673
msgid ""
"Reduces the unhappiness caused by aggressively deployed military units owned "
"by the city by 4 under Democracy and 2 under Republic -- in other words, it "
"neutralizes the unhappiness caused by two military units. This improvement "
"has no effect under other governments."
msgstr ""
"Lùghdaichidh seo am mì-thoileachas a dh'èirigheas an cois aonadan an airm "
"ann an àitichean ionnsaigheach a tha aig a' bhaile le 4 ann an deamocrasaidh "
"agus le 2 ann am poblachd -- no ann am facal eile, cuiridh e às dhan mhì-"
"thoileachas a dh'abharaicheas dà aonad an airm. Chan eil buaidh aig an "
"leasachadh seo fo riaghaltasan eile."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:914
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:950
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:977
msgid ""
"Before you can build any spaceship parts, you must build the Apollo Program."
msgstr ""
"Tha agad ri Prògram Apollo a thogail mus urrainn dhut co-phàirtean de "
"shoitheach-fànais a thogail."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1001
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Together with a Bank, a Stock Exchange boosts tax and luxury good production "
"in a city by 50%. Together with a Marketplace and a Bank, a Stock Exchange "
"boosts tax and luxury production in a city by 150%."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh margadh-earrannan am meud cinneasachadh chìsean is sòghalachd le 50% "
"sa bhaile ma bhios banca ann cuideachd. Ma bhios banca agus margaid ann "
"cuideachd, cuiridh margadh-earrannan am meud cinneasachadh chìsean is "
"sòghalachd le 150% sa bhaile."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1049
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the food resources by 100% on each farmland tile which is being "
"used around the city. Farmland tiles are those which have been irrigated a "
"second time."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud goireasan bìdh le 100% air gach leacag fearainn a "
"thathar a' cur gu feum mun cuairt air a' bhaile.  Tha leacagan fearainn 'nan "
"leacagan a chaidh uisgeachadh dà thuras."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1121
msgid ""
"Allows you to start building spaceship parts in cities with factories "
"(assuming you have researched the necessary technologies)."
msgstr ""
"Bheir seo comas dhut co-phàirtean airson soitheach-fànais a thogail ann am "
"bailtean far a bheil factaraidh (a' cur mar fhiacham gu bheil na "
"teicneolasan iomchaidh agad)."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1145
msgid ""
"City improvements which would normally have an upkeep of 1 are free of "
"upkeep, for all your cities on the same continent."
msgstr ""
"Bidh leasachadh baile sam bith a chosgadh 1 bheòshlaint a ghnàth saor an-"
"sgaidh airson gach baile agad air an dearbh mhòrthir."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1214
msgid ""
"This stunning technological achievement makes two content citizens happy in "
"all cities of all players who have researched Genetic Engineering. In the "
"unlikely event where there are not enough content citizens to benefit from "
"this effect in a city, the wonder applies to unhappy citizens (including "
"those unhappy about military activity), making each content then happy."
msgstr ""
"Nì an teicneolas iongantach seo dà shaoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte anns "
"gach baile aig na cluicheadairean uile a rannsaich einnseanaireachd "
"ghinteil. Ged nach tachair seo ro thric, mur eil saoranach riaraichte sam "
"bith ann a sheasas a bhuaidh, bidh buaidh air saoranaich mhì-thoilichte 'na "
"àite (a' gabhail a-steach an fheadhainn a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth "
"gnìomhachd an airm) agus nì iad riaraichte iad."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1241
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gives immediate technology advance the first time it is built by each player."
msgstr ""
"Bheir seo seachad dà adhartas teicneolais a' chiad turas a thogas "
"cluicheadair e."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each city on the same continent may support one unit free of shield upkeep."
msgstr ""
"'S urrainn do gach baile air an dearbh mhòrthir beòshlaint a thoirt do "
"dh'aon aonad saor an-asgaidh."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reduces corruption by 50% in all cities on the same continent."
msgstr ""
"Lùghdaichidh seo a' choirbteachd le 50% anns gach baile air an dearbh "
"mhòrthir."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1312
msgid "Works as a City Wall in all your cities on the same continent."
msgstr ""
"Tha seo mar gum biodh balla baile anns gach baile agad air an dearbh "
"mhòrthir."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1335
msgid ""
"Makes two content citizens happy in every city on the same continent. In the "
"unlikely event where there are no content citizens to get the effect of "
"Hanging Gardens, the wonder applies to unhappy citizens (including those "
"unhappy about military activity), making each content then happy."
msgstr ""
"Nì seo dà shaoranach riaraichte toilichte anns gach baile air an dearbh "
"mhòrthir. Ged nach tachair seo ro thric, mur eil saoranach riaraichte sam "
"bith ann a sheasas buaidh nan Liosan Crochte, bidh buaidh air saoranaich mhì-"
"thoilichte (a' gabhail a-steach an fheadhainn a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth "
"gnìomhachd an airm) agus nì iad riaraichte iad sa chiad dol a-mach agus an "
"uairsin toilichte."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1362
msgid ""
"Works as if you had a Hydro Plant in every city on the same continent. (This "
"reduces pollution and increases the effects of Factories and Mfg. Plants.)"
msgstr ""
"Tha buaidh aige seo mar gum biodh taigh dealain-uisge agad anns gach baile "
"air an dearbh mhòrthir. (Lùghdaichidh seo an truailleadh agus cuiridh e am "
"meud buaidh fhactaraidhean is thaighean-saothrachaidh.)"

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Boosts science production by 100% in every city on the same continent that "
"has a University."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh saidheansail le 100% anns gach baile air "
"an dearbh mhòrthir aig a bheil oilthigh."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1410
msgid ""
"Makes two unhappy citizens content in every city on the same continent "
"(including citizens unhappy about military activity)."
msgstr ""
"Nì seo dà shaoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte anns gach baile air an dearbh "
"mhòrthir (a' gabhail a-steach saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth "
"gnìomhachd an airm)."

#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:1458
