#: data/nation/dutch.ruleset:5
msgid "Dutch"
msgstr "Muinntir nan Tìrean Ìsle"

#: data/nation/dutch.ruleset:6
msgid "?plural:Dutch"
msgstr "?plural:Muinntir nan Tìrean Ìsle"

#: data/nation/dutch.ruleset:8
msgid ""
"When the Holy Roman Emperor sentenced the entire population to death, the "
"people of the Netherlands revolted and declared themselves independent, "
"forming the Union of Utrecht in 1579. The Netherlands grew to be a dominant "
"maritime and economic power in the 17th century."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a thug Impire Naomh na Ròimhe binn bàis air an sluagh gu lèir, "
"dh'èirich muinntir nan Tìrean Ìsle agus ghairm iad neo-eisimeileachd agus "
"stèidhich iad Aonadh Utrecht ann an 1579. Dh'fhàs na Tìrean Ìsle 'nan "
"cumhachd mara is malairt mhòr san 17mh linn."

