"Tha cus uisge ann am bogach agus tha seo 'na dhuilgheadas dhan àiteachas."

#: data/royale/terrain.ruleset:1059
#, fuzzy
msgid "?gui_type:Build Pre-Fortress/Fortress/Buoy"
