msgstr ""

#: data/royale/units.ruleset:3514
msgid ""
"The Cargo Aircraft is an airplane with an exceptionally high range while "
"carrying a heavy cargo. It is able to transport a wide range of units able "
"to surprise your enemy. This exceptionally heavy airplane has no offecive "
"capabilities but is able to defend."
msgstr ""

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:86
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A city with an Airport can airlift an extra unit per turn. Airlifting "
"instantly transports the unit from one city to another and will use  all of "
"the unit's movement points. A unit must have some movement  points left to "
"be airlifted, and cannot carry cargo."
msgstr ""
"'S urrainn do dhà bhaile anns a bheil puirt-adhair togail-adhair a dhèanamh "
"le aon aonad gach cuairt.  Ma nì thu togail-adhair, thèid an t-aonad a "
"ghluasad on dàrna bhaile gun bhaile eile agus cha bhi puingean gluasaid air "
"fhàgail aig an aonad.  Feumaidh puingean gluasaid a bhith aig aonad mus "
"urrainn dhut togail-adhair a dhèanamh leis."

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:91
msgid ""
"Two cities with Airports can airlift medium and heavy weight units once "
"Advanced Flight and Fusion Power are discovered."
msgstr ""

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:213
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Increases the luxury good and tax output in a city by an additional 50%. "
"With both a Bank and a Marketplace in a city, the total bonus is 100%."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh sòghalachd is cìsean a' bhaile le 50%."

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:474
msgid ""
"When any small city grows or shrinks, 10 food points are saved. This helps "
"cities to grow faster and more easily withstand famine. With a Granary this "
"is extended to cities of size 4 and above. (10 food points is half what a "
"small city needs to grow, but more points are needed for later growth steps.)"
msgstr ""

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:532 data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:672
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:863 data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1018
#, fuzzy, c-format
msgid ""
"Any kind of electrical plant increases the shield production effects of a "
"Factory or Mfg. Plant in its city by 25% each. Thus, an electrical plant in "
"combination with either a Factory or Mfg. Plant gives a 50% production bonus "
"over the level without any of these improvements. An electrical plant, "
"Factory, and Mfg. Plant together give a 100% production bonus. The extra "
"production may lead to the city generating more pollution."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud buaidh an fhactaraidh agus an taighe-saothrachaidh air "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan a' bhaile. Cuiridh taigh-cumhachd am meud "
"cinneasachadh sgiathan le 75% ma bhios factaraidh no taigh-saothrachaidh sa "
"bhaile thar na gheibheadh tu as aonais; gheibhear duais cinneasachaidh "
"150% an cois taigh-cumhachd, factaraidh agus taigh-saothrachaidh ann am "
"baile. Faodaidh gun adhbharaich an cinneasachadh a bharrachd seo barrachd "
"truaillidh ann."

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1153
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Increases the luxury good and tax output in a city by an additional 50%, or "
"100% if Super Highways are also in the city. A Marketplace, Bank, and Stock "
"Exchange together in a city yield a total bonus of 150%. Adding Super "
"Highways yields a total of 200%."
msgstr ""
"Cuiridh seo am meud cinneasachadh sòghalachd is cìsean a' bhaile le 50%."

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1385
#, fuzzy, c-format
msgid ""
"This stunning technological achievement makes one content citizen happy in "
"each of your cities (2 extra luxury goods per city). It further reduces your "
"risk of plague (by 10% of the base chance). With knowledge of Medicine, any "
"of your cities with an Aqueduct and a Sewer System will be entirely free of "
"plague."
msgstr ""
"Nì an teicneolas iongantach seo aon saoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte anns "
"gach baile agad (a' gabhail a-steach saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air "
"sgàth gnìomhachd an airm). Lùghdaichidh e cunnart tinneis sa bhaile "
"tuilleadh."

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1487
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Increases the defense of all your cities by adding a +50% bonus to its "
"units' intrinsic defense strength against land units (this is cumulative "
"with any City Walls), and preventing the loss of population which occurs "
"when a defending unit is defeated by a land unit."
msgstr ""
"Bidh e nas fhasa baile a dhìon ma bhios balla baile ann.  Bidh cumhachd dìon "
"de dh'aonadan am broinn baile trì turais nas àirde an aghaidh aonadan "
"talamhainn is heileacoptairean.  Chan eil iad gu feum an aghaidh aonadan "
"adhair is mara agus hòbhaitsearan.  Dìonaidh balla baile ro chall sluaigh "
"cuideachd a thachras nuair a thèid aonad dìon a sgriosadh le aonad "
"talamhainn."

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1905
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gives 1 additional luxury good to every city, and 6 luxuries to the city "
"where it is located."
msgstr ""
"Nì seo dà shaoranach mì-thoilichte riaraichte anns gach baile (a' gabhail a-"
"steach saoranaich a tha mì-thoilichte air sgàth gnìomhachd an airm)."

#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1956
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All your new military land units start with an additional veteran level "
"(this is cumulative with any Barracks building in a city. With both, units "
"are created as Hardened)."
msgstr ""
"Tòisichidh gach aonad talamhainn an airm ùr air a' chiad leibheil de sheann "
"ghaisgeachd ma thèid a thogail air an dearbh mhòrthir."

