#: server/commands.cpp:205
msgid "Turn on or off AI debugging of given entity."
msgstr "Cuir air no dheth dì-bhugadh de dh'eintiteas leis an IF."

#: server/commands.cpp:206
msgid ""
"Print AI debug information about given entity and turn continuous debugging "
"output for this entity on or off."
msgstr ""
"Clò-bhuail fiosrachadh dì-bhugaidh leis an IF mun eintiteas agus cuir air no "
"dheth an dì-bhugadh leantainneach airson an eintiteis seo."

#. TRANS: translate text between <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:211
msgid "set <option-name> <value>"
msgstr "set <ainm na roghainne> <luach>"

#: server/commands.cpp:211
msgid "Set server option."
msgstr "Suidhich roghainn an fhrithealaiche."

#. TRANS: don't translate text in ''
#: server/commands.cpp:213
msgid ""
"Set an option on the server. The syntax and legal values depend on the "
"option; see the help for each option. Some options are \"bitwise\", in that "
"they consist of a choice from a set of values; separate these with |, for "
"instance, '/set topology wrapx|iso'. For these options, use syntax like '/"
"set topology \"\"' to set no values."
msgstr ""
"Suidhich roghainn air an fhrithealaiche. Tha luachan a' cho-chàraidh agus an "
"lagha a' crochadh air an roghainn; thoir sùil air a' chobhair airson gach "
"roghainn. Tha cuide dhe na roghainnean seo \"bitwise\" agus 's ciall dha gu "
"bheil roghainn eadar seata de luachan ann; cuir | eatarra, mar eisimpleir '/"
"set topology wrapx|iso'. Cleachd co-chàradh mar '/set topology \"\"' anns na "
"roghainnean seo mur eil thu airson luach a shuidheachadh."

#. TRANS: translate text between <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:224
msgid "team <player> <team>"
msgstr "team <cluicheadair> <sgioba>"

#: server/commands.cpp:224
msgid "Change a player's team affiliation."
msgstr "Atharraich dàimh-sgioba de chluicheadair."

#: server/commands.cpp:225
msgid ""
"A team is a group of players that start out allied, with shared vision and "
"embassies, and fight together to achieve team victory with averaged "
"individual scores. Each player is always a member of a team (possibly the "
"only member). This command changes which team a player is a member of. Use "
"\"\" if names contain whitespace."
msgstr ""
"'S e buidheann de chluicheadairean a tha ann an sgioba aig a bhios "
"caidreachas. co-lèirsinn agus ambasaidean o thùs. Nì iad cogadh còmhla gus "
"buaidh sgioba a thoirt agus thèid cuibheas nan sgòr fa leth a thoirt do gach "
"cluicheadair. Bidh cluicheadair ann an sgioba an-còmhnaidh ach is mathaid "
"gur iad an aon chluicheadair san sgioba. Atharraichidh an àithne seo dè an "
"sgioba sa bhios gach cluicheadair. Cuir \"\" mun ainm ma tha àitichean bàna "
"ann."

#. TRANS: translate text between <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:234
msgid "rulesetdir <directory>"
msgstr "rulesetdir <eòlaire>"

#: server/commands.cpp:235
msgid "Choose new ruleset directory or modpack."
msgstr "Tagh eòlaire riaghailtean ùr no modpack."

#. TRANS: translate text between <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:239
msgid "metamessage <meta-line>"
msgstr "metamessage <meta-line>"

#: server/commands.cpp:239
msgid "Set metaserver info line."
msgstr "Suidhich loidhne fiosrachadh a' mheata-fhrithealaiche."

#: server/commands.cpp:240
msgid ""
"Set user defined metaserver info line. If parameter is omitted, previously "
"set metamessage will be removed. For most of the time user defined "
"metamessage will be used instead of automatically generated messages, if it "
"is available."
msgstr ""
"Suidhich loidhne fiosrachadh metaserver a thèid a shònrachadh le "
"cleachdaiche. Ma dh'fhàgar a-mach am paramadair, thèid am metamessage a "
"chaidh a shuidheachadh roimhe a thoirt air falbh. Thèid metamessage a thèid "
"a shònrachadh le cleachdaiche a chleachdadh mar is trice an àite "
"teachdaireachdan a chaidh a chruthachadh gu fèin-obrachail mur eil e ri "
"fhaighinn."

#. TRANS: translate text between <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:247
msgid "metapatches <meta-line>"
msgstr "metapatches <meta-line>"

#: server/commands.cpp:247
msgid "Set metaserver patches line."
msgstr "Suidhich loidhne brèidean a' mheata-fhrithealaiche."

#: server/commands.cpp:254
msgid "Control metaserver connection."
msgstr "Rianaich ceangal a' mheata-fhrithealaiche."

#: server/commands.cpp:255
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"'metaconnection ?' reports on the status of the connection to metaserver. "
"'metaconnection down' or 'metac d' brings the metaserver connection down. "
"'metaconnection up' or 'metac u' brings the metaserver connection up. "
"'metaconnection persistent' or 'metac p' is like 'up', but keeps trying "
"after failures. "
msgstr ""
"Tha 'metaconnection ?' ag aithisg air inbhe a' cheangail ris a' mheata-"
"fhrithealaiche. Cuiridh 'metaconnection down' no 'metac d' crìoch air a' "
"cheangal ris a' mheata-fhrithealaiche. Fosglaidh 'metaconnection up' or "
"'metac u' ceangal ris a' mheata-fhrithealaiche."

#. TRANS: translate text between <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:266
msgid "metaserver <address>"
msgstr "metaserver <seòladh>"

#: server/commands.cpp:267
msgid "Set address (URL) for metaserver to report to."
msgstr "Suidhich seòladh (URL) ris an nì am meata-fhrithealaiche aithisg."

#. TRANS: translate text between <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:271
msgid "aitoggle <player-name>"
msgstr "aitoggle <ainm a' chluicheadair>"

#: server/commands.cpp:271
msgid "Toggle AI status of player."
msgstr "Toglaich inbhe na h-IF de chluicheadair"

#. TRANS: translate text between [] and <> only
#: server/commands.cpp:275
msgid "take [connection-name] <player-name>"
msgstr "take [ainm-ceangail] <ainm a' chluicheadair>"

#: server/commands.cpp:276
msgid "Take over a player's place in the game."
msgstr "Rach an àite cluicheadair eile sa gheama."

#. TRANS: Don't translate text between ''
#: server/commands.cpp:278
msgid ""
"Only the console and connections with cmdlevel 'hack' can force other "
"connections to take over a player. If you're not one of these, only the "
"<player-name> argument is allowed. If '-' is given for the player name and "
"the connection does not already control a player, one is created and "
"assigned to the connection. The 'allowtake' option controls which players "
"may be taken and in what circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Chan fhaod ach an consol agus ceanglaichean leis a' cmdlevel 'hack' "
"ceanglaichean eile èigneachadh gus cluicheadair a ghabhail os làimh. Mur eil "
