#: server/settings.cpp:1421
#, fuzzy
msgid "Map topology"
msgstr "Clàr-amais topo-eòlas nam mapa"

#. TRANS: do not edit the ugly ASCII art
#: server/settings.cpp:1423
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Freeciv21 maps are always two-dimensional. They may wrap at the north-south "
"and east-west directions to form a flat map, a cylinder, or a torus (donut). "
"Individual tiles may be rectangular or hexagonal, with either an overhead "
"(\"classic\") or isometric alignment.\n"
"To play with a particular topology, clients will need a matching tileset.\n"
"Overhead rectangular:      Isometric rectangular:\n"
"      _________               /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|             /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|             \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|             /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"                             \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"Hex:                       Iso-hex:\n"
"  /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\               _   _   _   _   _\n"
"  | | | | | | |             / \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\\n"
"  \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\             \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/\n"
"   | | | | | | |            / \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\\n"
"   \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/             \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/\n"
msgstr ""
"Tha mapaichean Freeciv 2D an-còmhnaidh. Bidh iad air am pasgadh aig oir an "
"tuath 's an deas no an ear 's an iar a chum mapa rèidh, siolandair no donut. "
"Bidh cruth ceart-cheàrnagach no sia-cheàrnach air na leacagan, ann an rian "
"clasaigeach no ioso-meatrach - bu chòir dhut sin a shuidheachadh a-rèir "
"seata nan leacagan a chleachdar.\n"
"Ceart-chèarnagach clasaigeach:  Ceart-chèarnagach ioso-meatrach:\n"
"      _________                             /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|                           /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|                           \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\\n"
"     |_|_|_|_|_|                           /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\n"
"                                           \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/ \n"
"Leacagan sia-cheàrnach:        Iosa-m. is sia-cheàrnach:\n"
"  /\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\                             _   _   _   _   _ \n"
"  | | | | | | |                           / \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\\n"
"  \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\                           \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/\n"
"   | | | | | | |                          / \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\\n"
"   \\/\\/\\/\\/\\/\\/                           \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/ \\_/\n"

