#, fuzzy
#~ msgid ""
#~ "First tech researched: You have gained your first technology! "
#~ "Technological advances are an integral concept in Freeciv21. As you "
#~ "increase your technology level new units, buildings, governments, and "
#~ "various free bonuses will become available to you. For now, go over into "
#~ "the Research report and play around a little. Press F6 to open the "
#~ "Research report [or click on the Research tab]. Find the technology "
