#, fuzzy
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Second tech researched: Now you have gained your second technology. Go "
#~ "back into the Research report (F6) and take a quick look at your "
#~ "progress. If you set Republic as your technology goal earlier, a new "
#~ "research target should have been chosen for you automatically. If you do "
