#, fuzzy
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Republic: You have successfully completed research to The Republic. This "
#~ "technology is particularly useful because it allows a new form of "
#~ "government. The government your civilization follows is very important in "
#~ "determining your development. In the beginning you started in Despotism, "
#~ "a very inefficient form of government. Later government options will give "
#~ "you some choice of whether your civilization is to be a peaceful trading "
#~ "nation or a conquering juggernaut. Each has advantages and disadvantages. "
